## building a chroot

### preparing a ruby for the chroot

Grab a Ruby and untar it, cd into it and

    .configure --prefix=/ruby; make; sudo make install

### building

pass the Ruby prefix with --rp

    sudo ./bin/build.rb -v --rp /ruby target

